metadata.name: SEIZER IS gradient
metadata.description: This is a digital rendering of an original print released in 2013.  This print is an attempt to identify who I am. SEIZER ONE is love & integrity, never ending art, persistence, creative thought honest, real, participation, and contribution.  The first owner of this NFT will receive a physical sold out print signed and numbered by the artist. This piece is an MP4 @ 1080 X 1350
